01:30:53.120 --> 01:30:56.582
They'll teach you...

01:30:57.166 --> 01:31:00.670
like I shouldn't have
given my gun up, and...

01:31:00.795 --> 01:31:05.132
things you should do,
and things I didn't do.

01:31:07.593 --> 01:31:09.095
Go on.

01:31:09.220 --> 01:31:12.598
That's it. I don't know.

01:31:12.765 --> 01:31:15.601
I think I'm gonna like this job.

01:31:17.186 --> 01:31:20.731
My partner, Oscar, is the best.

01:31:22.983 --> 01:31:25.986
I think I'm gonna like working with him.

01:31:29.657 --> 01:31:33.994
It's finally a matter of knowing them.
These pickpockets are a closed fraternity.

01:31:34.120 --> 01:31:36.497
You get so you know them,
or you know the type.

01:31:36.622 --> 01:31:38.738
After a while, you get
to like the crazy job.

01:31:38.863 --> 01:31:41.102
Anything for a change, Oscar?

01:31:41.227 --> 01:31:44.463
You ought to see a chiropractor
about that sore neck of yours.

01:31:44.588 --> 01:31:48.509
