01:32:10.197 --> 01:32:13.492
How about you circling over by the counter
in case he hits and runs?

01:32:13.617 --> 01:32:17.788
I need a new watchband anyway.
Maybe I'll buy one while I'm there.

01:32:52.573 --> 01:32:56.035
Welcome back to The Dating Game,
Connie, you now must make a decision,

01:32:56.160 --> 01:33:00.414
The gentlemen over there
have done their best to win your heart,

01:33:03.417 --> 01:33:05.294
You said good-bye to the gambling man?

01:33:05.419 --> 01:33:07.546
He asked me
if I wanted to play some poker.

01:33:07.672 --> 01:33:10.091
Can you believe that?

01:33:13.594 --> 01:33:18.099
Yard time, coming in,

01:33:45.793 --> 01:33:49.088
Guard said I'm gonna die tomorrow.

01:33:56.429 --> 01:33:59.265
I'm gonna die to save you.

01:34:02.226 --> 01:34:04.270
I'm gonna die...

01:34:04.812 --> 01:34:07.648
like Jesus Christ.

01:34:20.494 --> 01:34:23.706
They'll sew him up
and put him in a straightjacket tonight.

01:34:23.831 --> 01:34:27.335
Tomorrow morning, he'll be nice
and healthy when they kill him.

01:34:27.460 --> 01:34:30.963
Smell the gas in the air
for days and days.

01:34:33.215 --> 01:34:35.843
Powell can save your life.

01:34:35.968 --> 01:34:40.306
We're all getting new trials.
Believe me.

01:34:42.558 --> 01:34:43.726
Lock up!

01:34:43.851 --> 01:34:46.562
Final lock up,

01:34:46.687 --> 01:34:50.858
Stand in front of your cell door
for the final lock up,

01:34:54.904 --> 01:34:58.032
Count time in the east block,
Count time,

01:34:58.157 --> 01:35:00.826
Turn on your cell lights,
Stand at the cell bars,

01:35:00.951 --> 01:35:03.704
Stand clear!

01:35:20.054 --> 01:35:22.473
Greg, please.

01:35:23.516 --> 01:35:27.061
I wanna be your...

01:35:28.020 --> 01:35:30.439
I'm sorry.

01:35:30.564 --> 01:35:33.192
We was friends.

01:35:33.776 --> 01:35:36.070
We was brothers.

01:35:38.656 --> 01:35:42.076
If I had only did what you told me.

01:35:42.660 --> 01:35:45.788
It's all my fault.

01:35:53.838 --> 01:35:58.092
Do you finally understand
that you shot that cop when he was down?

01:35:58.217 --> 01:36:01.429
No matter what your mind
lets you remember?

01:36:03.305 --> 01:36:08.352
I must've did it if you said so.

01:36:10.229 --> 01:36:13.232
I want to be your friend.

01:36:15.276 --> 01:36:18.320
We was like family.

01:36:53.356 --> 01:36:56.484
Just a minute, sir.

01:36:57.443 --> 01:37:00.988
You forgot your change.

01:37:01.197 --> 01:37:03.616
Thank you for coming in.

01:37:15.836 --> 01:37:17.880
Thank you.

01:37:21.842 --> 01:37:26.847
Do you want to sign your resignation
papers or fight the charge against you?

01:37:30.810 --> 01:37:36.232
- Sir, what if I don't sign?
- You'll be charged with shoplifting.

01:37:36.357 --> 01:37:39.485
The witness is positive,
so you'll possibly be found guilty...

01:37:39.610 --> 01:37:42.613
and get fired from the department.

01:37:42.947 --> 01:37:48.035
Then you might find yourself
in criminal court on a petty theft charge.

01:37:49.036 --> 01:37:51.080
Captain, what should I do?

01:37:51.205 --> 01:37:55.793
Officer, if you're guilty,
there's only one thing to do.

01:38:03.009 --> 01:38:05.428
Are you guilty?

01:38:54.685 --> 01:38:57.480
You're not a thief.

01:39:08.574 --> 01:39:11.285
You have no idea.

01:39:11.952 --> 01:39:14.872
