to sit and be silent.

01:43:20.951 --> 01:43:23.412
Counsel for the defense refused...

01:43:23.537 --> 01:43:26.665
but said that he wanted it
read into the record...

01:43:26.791 --> 01:43:31.587
that he was deemed to have been
forced to sit and be silent.

01:43:32.755 --> 01:43:34.799
"Deemed."

01:43:35.549 --> 01:43:37.259
That's when it hit me.

01:43:37.385 --> 01:43:41.764
Physical fact is meaningless.
Lawyers can deem that fantasy is real.

01:43:41.889 --> 01:43:43.599
Lie is truth.

01:43:43.724 --> 01:43:46.435
Now Jimmy Smith's decided
he wants a brand new lawyer.

01:43:46.560 --> 01:43:49.438
I guess it'll take a few more weeks...

01:43:49.563 --> 01:43:53.734
for the new lawyer to acquaint himself
with the case and...

01:43:57.655 --> 01:44:00.282
So I decided to quit the law.

01:44:01.200 --> 01:44:02.618
I'm finished.

01:44:02.743 --> 01:44:06.914
Why don't you take some time
and think about it, Phil?

01:44:11.002 --> 01:44:13.963
Campbell's forgotten.
He may as well never have lived.

01:44:14.088 --> 01:44:16.424
Hettinger's a ghost.

01:44:16.882 --> 01:44:19.635
Only the legal process has meaning.

01:44:20.094 --> 01:44:22.430
I've got to get away.

01:44:22.555 --> 01:44:25.266
You know what I was thinking?

01:44:26.308 --> 01:44:28.853
I was thinking
that if it were in my power...

01:44:28.978 --> 01:44:32.189
I'd release Powell and Smith,
drop all the charges.

01:44:32.314 --> 01:44:34.734
Let 'em walk.

01:44:36.777 --> 01:44:41.115
If only I could send some lawyers
and judges to the gas chamber.

01:44:48.706 --> 01:44:52.376
How about going out
for some Mexican food tonight?

01:44:53.127 --> 01:44:56.505
You can afford to support a husband
and children...

01:44:56.630 --> 01:44:59.550
